('JTSN-CARRIER-Y-C17', 'CARRIER-Y-C17', 'Jetson Series', 'Carrier Board Y-C17', E'กะทัดรัด Orin NX/Nano 85x63x18mm (45g) เปิดอัตโนมัติ -40 ถึง +85°C\n\nCompact for Orin NX/Nano. 85x63x18mm (45g). Auto power-on. -40 to +85°C.\n\nSpecs: Module: Orin NX/Nano | Size: 85x63x18mm (45g)', 'บอร์ดพื้นฐาน Carrier Board', 0, 'rfq', 'carrier-y-c17', '/jetson-images/carrier-boards/y-c17-1.jpg', ARRAY['/jetson-images/carrier-boards/y-c17-1.jpg']::text[], ARRAY['nvidia','jetson','edge-ai','carrier-boards']::text[], false, true, 12, 'carry_in'),
('JTSN-CARRIER-Y-C13', 'CARRIER-Y-C13', 'Jetson Series', 'Carrier Board Y-C13', E'สำหรับ AGX Orin/Xavier 2x RJ45, USB, HDMI, MiniPCIe, M.2, GPIO\n\nFor AGX Orin/Xavier. 2x RJ45, 4x USB, HDMI, 2x MiniPCIe, M.2, GPIO. -40 to +85°C.\n\nSpecs: Module: AGX Orin/Xavier | AI: Up to 275 TOPS', 'บอร์ดพื้นฐาน Carrier Board', 0, 'rfq', 'carrier-y-c13', '/jetson-images/carrier-boards/y-c13-1.png', ARRAY['/jetson-images/carrier-boards/y-c13-1.png']::text[], ARRAY['nvidia','jetson','edge-ai','carrier-boards']::text[], false, true, 12, 'carry_in'),
('JTSN-CARRIER-Y-C11', 'CARRIER-Y-C11', 'Jetson Series', 'Carrier Board Y-C11', E'กะทัดรัดสำหรับ Orin NX/Nano\n\nCompact for Orin NX/Nano modules.\n\nSpecs: Module: Orin NX/Nano', 'บอร์ดพื้นฐาน Carrier Board', 0, 'rfq', 'carrier-y-c11', '/jetson-images/carrier-boards/y-c11.png', ARRAY['/jetson-images/carrier-boards/y-c11.png']::text[], ARRAY['nvidia','jetson','edge-ai','carrier-boards']::text[], false, true, 12, 'carry_in'),
('JTSN-CARRIER-Y-C9', 'CARRIER-Y-C9', 'Jetson Series', 'Carrier Board Y-C9', E'สำหรับโมดูล AGX Xavier\n\nFor AGX Xavier module.\n\nSpecs: Module: AGX Xavier', 'บอร์ดพื้นฐาน Carrier Board', 0, 'rfq', 'carrier-y-c9', '/jetson-images/carrier-boards/y-c9.png', ARRAY['/jetson-images/carrier-boards/y-c9.png']::text[], ARRAY['nvidia','jetson','edge-ai','carrier-boards']::text[], false, true, 12, 'carry_in'),
('JTSN-CARRIER-Y-C8', 'CARRIER-Y-C8', 'Jetson Series', 'Carrier Board Y-C8', E'AGX Orin/Xavier I/O หลากหลาย\n\nFor AGX Orin/Xavier with rich I/O.\n\nSpecs: Module: AGX Orin/Xavier', 'บอร์ดพื้นฐาน Carrier Board', 0, 'rfq', 'carrier-y-c8', '/jetson-images/carrier-boards/y-c8.png', ARRAY['/jetson-images/carrier-boards/y-c8.png']::text[], ARRAY['nvidia','jetson','edge-ai','carrier-boards']::text[], false, true, 12, 'carry_in'),
